{"tid":805991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix節目玩福島「核旅遊」 日或提控","createTime":"2018-09-04T10:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T12:24:11.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dccf57926b7b6a3cdf4af7ea8ace2bd15f7505ae","tid":805991,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"美國影視串流平台Netflix一套名為《非一般旅程》（Dark Tourist）的紀錄片，最近被日本政府復興廳及福島縣政府盯上，指紀錄片有可能製造對當地的「不必要」恐慌。當局正研究影片，並考慮進一步行動。<br />\n質疑當地仍受輻射污染<br />\n《非一般旅程》的新西蘭拍攝者法里爾在節目中，進入了2011年日本311大地震中受災最嚴重的福島縣，探討當地的「核旅遊」問題。他在節目中多番質疑當地是否仍受輻射污染，包括質疑在距離發生核輻射洩漏的福島第一核電廠20公里範圍內的浪江町內一間餐廳的食物有否受輻射污染。<br />\n法里爾在影片中亦進入了沒有准許證不能進入的禁區，他和同行團友在旅遊巴上偵測到輻射強度讀數逐步增高，甚至比烏克蘭切爾諾貝爾核災禁區更高，展露不安情緒。片中導遊更指因為當地已宣佈緊急狀態，所以日本政府才可以提高當地的允許輻射量，讓遊客進入當地。<br />\n福島縣政府表示正審視影片內容，並與在311大地震後成立的復興廳合作，考慮進一步行動。在同一集中，法里爾亦有到日本的「自殺森林」青木原樹海，而另一集則他就到哈薩克，在核試形成的湖泊中游泳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180903/20490593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180903%2F20490593&d=4LxgvR7ehd5k%2F1H1t1yFw4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2d22ac52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180903%2F20490593&h=77cf2333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180903/20490593</a>"},{"pid":"df13dac45268c1a7d81d3221b0e46c2deac9709c","tid":805991,"uid":199211,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"崩口人忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f50b8b3c2b85947a372369d70f4fd78120d306","tid":805991,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:24:11.000Z","msg":"日本政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2aceee1dd63c4408db809937f241acdc2f3a43","tid":805991,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"但我都想去下"},{"pid":"61f431393ceb5baed617ece66e100a53ebd9929d","tid":805991,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"之前有好多連登仔撐偷入福島禁區冇問題嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29506ae904f4e6c0be5b0aebdee2129e2d55d563","tid":805991,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61f431393ceb5baed617ece66e100a53ebd9929d","tid":805991,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"之前有好多連登仔撐偷入福島禁區冇問題嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:57:43.000Z","msg":"on9連登仔係包拗頸姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e4af859f13620c49ef0171ac01635498682c54","tid":805991,"uid":60655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"去美帝告誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590a0657291a750356e4b61ad15f7a77a7563533","tid":805991,"uid":24345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"套野個idea好但個主持好撚濕鳩，係咁套自己睇法落人地到<br />\n<br />\n有一集去英國有到搞戰爭festival ，一年一度扮二戰嗰啲，條撚樣係咁同著Nazi衫嘅人講你唔覺得有問題咩你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952f71ac444fc2f0d75734455f5c8b44cd550bea","tid":805991,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"咁小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj